data.description:
Discover the perfect blend of comfort, luxury, and outdoor adventure in this remarkable 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom split-level home, nestled against the serene backdrop of Steve Machaud Park. Situated on an oversized lot, this property offers an extraordinary outdoor experience with a sport court featuring a lit half basketball court that transforms into a winter wonderland for ice skating enthusiasts.
The backyard is an outdoor oasis, complete with a cozy fire pit, providing a picturesque setting for gatherings and wildlife views that captivate the senses. Step inside to find a freshly updated walk-out basement with new flooring and a pristine coat of paint, creating an inviting space for relaxation and entertainment.
